Package lib.lists

Class LinkedList.LinearNode<T>

java.lang.Object
lib.lists.LinkedList.LinearNode<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of element held in this node
Enclosing class:
LinkedList<T>
public static class LinkedList.LinearNode<T>
extends java.lang.Object
Represents a node in a linked data structure where each node contains an element and a reference to the next node in the sequence.
